## Summary

Produced 5 artifacts for `kanban-view` planning phase at `specs/kanban-view/`:

| Artifact | Content |
|---|---|
| `research.md` | Existing-code patterns (Dashboard data flow, FeatureCard chrome, types, e2e conventions), library choices (Tailwind-only, sessionStorage hook, pure grouping fn), 6 rejected alternatives |
| `data-model.md` | `FeatureSummary` (unchanged consumer), `PhaseColumn` (UI-only derived), `ViewPreference` (sessionStorage); invariants, state transitions, integrity rules |
| `contracts/GET-api-features.md` | Unchanged endpoint contract — documents single-fetch invariant (CON-007/AC-016) |
| `plan.md` | Summary, technical context, constitution check (10/10 ✅), project structure, 6 component designs, constraint verification map (9/9 CONs traced), cross-component consistency matrix (12 shared values traced), per-component test strategy, agent failure mode checks, quality checkpoints, quickstart |
| `tasks.md` | 8 tasks in 7 phases: shared infra (T001-T003) → P1 board components + Dashboard wiring (T004-T005) → regression fix (T006) → P3 overflow tests (T007) → final gate (T008). Every task has exact file paths, done conditions, test level, constraint refs, agent failure mode checks |

**Key design decisions:**
- Extract `statusColors` → `badgeStyles.ts` (CON-006 parity, shared by FeatureCard + KanbanCard)
- `groupFeaturesByPhase` pure fn with `other` bucket for unknown phases (CON-009, AC-011 unit test)
- `useSessionView` hook, default `'board'`, try/catch around sessionStorage (FR-002/FR-003)
- Board consumes `useQuery(['features'])` via props — no second fetch (CON-007)
- `app.spec.ts` bounded regression fix: click List toggle before `feature-card-*` assertions (default flipped to Board)
- Zero new runtime deps, zero backend changes (CON-003, FR-016)

**Constraint coverage**: all 9 CONs mapped to design decisions + verification checkpoints. All 22 ACs traced to tasks. No questions.json needed — spec resolved all ambiguities via documented assumptions.
